summary: Our office is located in the heart of Scottsdale. We are in the McCormick Ranch area and just a few miles from the town of Paradise Valley, Arizona. Our team of real estate agents are located through out the valley and we can service sellers and buyers in all of the Phoenix metro area. We are a boutique real estate company that offers service the old fashion way with technology of today. We are experience at luxury homes to first time buyers/sellers. If you are looking to sale or buy you have found the right place to start.We are currently looking for talented agents that would like to work for the number one company in the world with a boutique atmosphere. You are not just another agent here. Contact us for a cup of coffee and a private conversation to see if we are the right place for you.
